obj_root_law_sections_1:
  object
  (str sectionId) (str 68912)
  (str sectionNo) (str 1)
  (str orderNo) (int 1)
  (str title) (str `Extension of Regulations and Acts in force in Saharanpur to Dehra Dun.`)
  (str content) (str `The Regulations
and Acts now in force in the district of Saharanpur are hereby declared to extend to the said district of Dehra
Dun ^1***.`)
  (str footnotes) (str `1. The words “and no judgment heretofore given, order passed or proceeding had in the said district, shall be deemed to have been
or to be invalid merely because any Regulation or Act, under or in reference to which such judgment, order or proceeding was
given, passed or had, was not in force at the time of such judgment, order or proceeding, was given, passed or had, was not in
force at the time of such judgement, order or proceeding, or on the ground of a defect of jurisdiction in ay Court or office” rep.
by Act 12 of 1891.`)
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218&sectionId=68912&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218)
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  object
  (str sectionId) (str 68913)
  (str sectionNo) (str 2)
  (str orderNo) (int 2)
  (str title) (str `Jurisdiction of High Court and Board of Revenue over Dehra Dun.`)
  (str content) (str `The High Court and
the Board of Revenue of ^1[Uttar Pradesh] shall exercise ^2*** respectively, in the said district, all the powers
which the said High Court or Board of Revenue are at present, respectively, authorized to exercise in any
part of ^1[Agra].`)
  (str footnotes) (str `1. Subs, by the A. O. 1950 for "the North-Western Provinces".

2. The words "and shall be deemed to have been heretofore authorized to exercise" rep., ibid.`)
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218&sectionId=68913&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218)
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  object
  (str sectionId) (str 68914)
  (str sectionNo) (str 3)
  (str orderNo) (int 3)
  (str title) (str `District Court of Saharanpur to be District Court of Dehra Dun.`)
  (str content) (str `The District Court of
Saharanpur shall be ^1*** the District Court of such district until the State Government otherwise directs
^2***.`)
  (str footnotes) (str `1. The words “deemed to have been heretofore the District Court of the said district of Dehra Dun and” rep., ibid.

2. The words “and may subject to the provisions of Act 6 of 1871, hear appeals from decisions given in the said district before
the passing of this Act” rep. by Act 12 of 1891The words “and may subject to the provisions of Act 6 of 1871, hear appeals from decisions given in the said district before
the passing of this Act” rep. by Act 12 of 1891`)
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218&sectionId=68914&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218)
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  object
  (str sectionId) (str 68915)
  (str sectionNo) (str 4)
  (str orderNo) (int 4)
  (str title) (str `Exemption of Jaunsar Bawar.`)
  (str content) (str `Nothing in this Act shall apply to that portion of the Dehra Dun
district called ^1Jaunsar Bawar ^2***`)
  (str footnotes) (str `1. “Jaunsar Bawar” was one of the Scheduled Districts of the State of Uttar Pradesh, see the Scheduled Districts Act, 1874 (14 of
1874), First Schedule, Pt. IV, but has ceased to be so under the Constitution of India.

2. The words “and referred to in s. 11 of Act 24 of 1864” rep. by Act 12 of 1891.`)
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218&sectionId=68915&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00092_187121_1661923541218)
